#

Cream of Mushroom Soup

40 min
$5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

soupcreamycomfort food

Description

A rich and creamy mushroom soup that is perfect for a comforting meal, packed with umami flavor.

Ingredients

  • mushrooms, sliced: 8 ounces
  • onion, chopped: 1 medium
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • thyme, dried: 1 teaspoon
